channel.title: [PI][REF] Just a Client with some 699 sprites Take a look:)
channel.description:
Please post a Feedback:$
Hi, this is my project,
Soo i release this messy shit.
What ive done so far is: Made it Webclient Ready. New Compass New Orbs Tutorial of a new mapback because i started with Normal Pi client that has 474 interface, Did galkons tutorial for Tabarea & icons Edited the Tabarea, Tabhover & Tabclicked Files Edited the chatbox so it fits perfect with the tabarea Added new Chatbuttons + hovers Changed the Attack sprites Special attack tutorial Edited the skills interface via cache.(Forget the icons) Equipment tab has new Stones and buttons Added/Edited the Rules interface Added/Edited the Starter interface Edited the buttons for Friends,Clan chat, ignore etc option tab has 699 sprites Forget to add a sprite for logout xD Removed flames Changed the Background Added new arrows for Make-over thing
~~Known Bug~~ The bank interface got wrong some wrong positions Via cache not Rsinterface.Java
but this is how it looks so far. Put the RunescapeCache Folder in C:/ (Sorry bout RunescapeCache, the project had no name.)
Want to help me with the project??
